Description:
MODERN LIVING IN TIMBERTOP ESTATE
A modern feel and neutral tonings compliment the light and bright flowing floorplan of this four bedroom home.
Stemming from the wide long entry hall is an internal access door to the double garage providing security and protection from the weather.
The master suite is street facing with double entry doors, plantation shutters on the windows, a deep walk through robe to the large ensuite which has double basins and separate WC room.
Desirably, the kitchen is indeed the central heart of the home, overlooking the lounge and dining areas. Comprising plenty of bench space, a large walk in pantry with light, 900mm s.s appliances, mirrored splashbacks, dishwasher, pendant lighting, stone benchtops and large fridge cavity.
In addition to the lounge and dining areas adjacent the kitchen, there is additional living space in the theatre room, which could also be used as a fifth bedroom.
Remaining bedrooms are at the rear off the small back hall, each have built in robes, and are serviced by the main bathroom and separate toilet.
The laundry room is fabulous boasting workable space on the long benchtop, and plenty of storage in the under numerous bench cupboards and tall double built in robes.
Additional features include –
- Study nook
- Gas ducted heating
- Wall mount cooling
- Low maintenance grassed yard area
- Undercover alfresco for entertaining and outdoor enjoyment
- Inbuilt gas log fireplace for beautiful warmth and ambiance
- Wall mounted television
Walk to St Brigid's Primary School, Hicks Reserve playground, nearby to St Francis Xavier School, Officer Primary School, D'Angelos winery, public transport routes and surrounded by parks and walking tracks.
Just a short drive to Beaconsfield shops
Your new place to call home is nestled away in the quiet back streets of the Timbertop estate and awaits your inspection.

Description:
Theres no place like home! DIRECTIONS TO GET TO THE HOUSE IS BELOW
Enter- Grandvue Blvd, through the round about, left at Clendon Drive, right at Raleigh Way, left at Skyline Drive, right at Heyington Way, left at Avondale Street, right at Mowbray Street.
This appealing Metricon family home is just 3 years young, presents a functional design and stunning street appeal - there's an abundance of space and style from the façade through to the backyard.
This home offers four superb bedrooms and two separate living zones, including a master suite complete with walk in robes and ensuite, the remaining three bedrooms boast an ample amount of floorspace and built in robes serviced by the shared bathroom and separate toilet to accommodate family and guests.
Leading through to the open plan kitchen, living and dining it offers a practical lay out and features quality appliances that include 900mm oven/ stove top, dishwasher, plenty of cupboards as well as a walk-in pantry for additional storage space.
Internal features include; ducted heating, evaporative cooling, downlights, low maintenance flooring throughout perfect for asthmatics, alarm system, Foxtel connection to both living zones, internal & external access and a double remote-control garage.
Sliding doors open to the low maintenance rear yard and pergola area creating the perfect space for entertaining and relaxing.
Set in the highly desired Grandvue Estate in officer, close to St Francis Xavier College and a just short distance to the Arena shopping centre with Woolworths and a variety of take away options, M1 freeway and Cardinia train station are all nearby. Be sure to inspect as this one will not last long.

Description:
Living The Lifestyle On Lyntonlee
Your dream home has arrived! This newly built quality home in one Officers most sought-after locations is ready for you to move right in! From the moment you walk through the commanding front door into the spacious entry, you feel the sense of luxe that has been created here with 9ft ceilings, large square cornices, modern pendant light and stunning floorboards!
A perfect fusion of classic and contemporary the home showcases an impressive kitchen featuring dark shaker-style cabinetry with contrasting 40mm stone benchtops. It has 900mm appliances, soft-closing cabinetry throughout, a pull-out bin, a dishwasher and a very large butlers pantry! (You wont be short on storage!) The living area is a great size and looks out to the tiled alfresco with timber-lined ceiling.
The three generously sized bedrooms all feature plush carpets and walk-in-robes. The master (which is comparable to a home magazine bedroom!) is complemented by a huge walk-in-robe (more storage!) and through the other side of the robe is the sophisticated ensuite. Double vanity with custom cabinetry and stone tops, wall-to-ceiling tiles in the double shower, and a separate toilet. The main bathroom also has custom cabinetry with stone benchtops, tiled shower plus a bath.
Externally the home is low-maintenance and fully landscaped with synthetic turf in the rear yard no mowing required! Designer bricks, a double-garage, and exposed aggregate driveway to appeal to your desire for quality. A split system, ducted heating and very spacious laundry all add to the conveniences you would expect from a home of this calibre. Further to that, the home is close to shops, schools, parks and public transport.
Dont waste a minute. Set up your life of luxury living now! Call Sarah or Syarif today.

Description:
One the whole family can enjoy!
Introducing this immaculately presented home which comprises of every extra inclusion you could imagine that will truly take your breath away and excite every buyer who comes through the front door.
From the front façade to the outdoors, this home will not disappoint. Starting with the basics, this home offers four bedrooms, two bathrooms, (including ensuite). Walk in robe to master and built in robes to secondary bedrooms. Many would argue that the open plan kitchen, dining and living zone is the true heart of any home which is certainly showcased here to capture the ultimate family feel. In this impressive kitchen you will find; 900mm oven/cooktop, dishwasher, walk-in pantry and an abundance of cupboard storage space.
The excellent floor plan compliments family living and entertaining perfectly. With an additional living zone/rumpus room allowing for extra space for larger families not to mention the huge covered alfresco area flowing on from the family meals area making it a breeze to entertain family and friends or to host any occasion from the comfort of your own home. Set on a 375m2 allotment with an extremely easy to maintain yard with a double remote-control garage for secure parking or additional storage space.
Interior inclusions showcase, brand new carpet through-out, premium floor tiles, laundry, ducted heating, split system heating/cooling and a fresh coat of paint throughout.
Positioned in the Arcadia Estate, this home is within walking distance to the following amenities; Cardinia Railway Station, Lakeside Square Town Centre, Officer Town Centre and the desirable Officer Club. The position offers further appeal by being walking distance to schools, childcare and medical centre, as well as easy access to the M1 freeway.
This home will not disappoint, nor last long! If youd like to arrange a private inspection contact us today.

Description:
Design Excellence with Quality and Versatility!
Premium features, flexible living zones and impeccable presentation highlight the appeal of this modern double-storey home sitting on a generous sized block of 610m2 (approx) delivering an exceptional family lifestyle in a popular growing neighbourhood.

Impressive interior showcases five bedrooms all featuring stylish en suites, study and modern separate powder room. Impressive kitchen featuring only the finest quality stainless steel appliances, spacious butlers pantry, stone bench tops with ample cupboard space throughout the kitchen.

Call us today to call this dream home yours!
